Sinew/Otyebis Staff:



Sinew's golden optics simply watched Grimlock silently, a red ball of energy 
forming in his left hand.  With an internal command, a small hatch in the 
side of the Otyebis opened up.  Eight armed humanoid soldiers leapt out of 
the hatch, rocket packs activating.  All eight of them with their laser 
rifles headed towards Grimlock.

Sinew threw the red ball of laser energy at Grimlock.  "Leave or die.  It's 
that simple Cybertronian."
